high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Open the cabinet under the right sink and put the knife on the plate in the cabinet.
Pick up the plate with knife from the cabinet under the right sink.
Bring the plate with knife to the left sink.
Put the plate with knife in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with knife in the left sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife to the right of the sink.
Put the knife on the plate in the right cabinet under the sink.
Place the plate in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife on it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, and go forward to go to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter, adjacent to the sink.
Put the butter knife on the pan, in the cabinet under the right sink basin.
Pick up the pan with the butter knife in it.
Go to the left sink basin.
Put the pan in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a butter knife in it in the sink.
